reviewText: I love it as a kid and I love watching the Dvds>
The series was a childhood favorite, and just as good as I remember.
I'm so please and I can not wait to have the fourth season when it's available,thanks so much from Australia !!!!!!

Arrived in time.  Was as Shown. But did not work on regular Dvd player I have. Great Dvd.  Would Recommend it.
Packaging was great.  Thanks!
what a wonderful series. we have enjoyed so much.remember all the wonderful tv animal shows we enjoyed as children.  Yea

Thank you so much for making another season of Daktari: the 3rd season available!! My favorite show growing up! So thrilled to revisit this series our whole family loved! Have already purchased seasons 1 and 2 and have been very pleased! Quality of dvd's is excellent! Bring on season 4 as soon as possible! Pam Spencer.
It was as good as I remembered it. When will all the other seasons come out?
We are still waiting to see Season 4 - please bring out the last episodes as soon as possible.

I loved this show growing up and have been so pleased to get the DVDs.  I now own Season 1, 2, and 3 and hope Season 4 (the last season - if I remember correctly) comes out soon.  These are high quality dvds.  I have been VERY satisfied!  I highly recommend this season and the first 2 to anyone who loved Daktari or anyone who likes a great family show and wildlife.  Please has Season 4 Available ASAP!
